<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN""http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd"><html xmlns=http:<head><meta http-equiv=Content-Type content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><meta name=robots content=noindex,nofollow><title>Customers Email Review-Highlights Travel</title></head><style>table td ul{padding-left:20px}table td ul li{list-style-type:square;padding-left:0px;line-height:22 px;margin-bottom:15px;font-size: 16px;}p{font-size: 16px;}</style><body style="color: #999; margin: 40px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Cailibri, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;"><table width=600 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0 align=center style="margin: 10px auto; background: #f6f6f6;"><tr><td colspan=4><div style="background: url(https://images.highlightstravel.com/allpicture/2025/06/914c5e88afa240ea8cc887eb497cc506_cut_226x118_241_1750256468.jpg) no-repeat #f6f6f6 15px 0;height: 83px;background-size: contain;"></div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=4><img src="https://data.highlightstravel.com/image/forms/ah-newsletter-thankyou-top.jpg"></td></tr><tr><td style="text-align: center;color: #ad1818;font-size: 25px;font-weight: 600;padding-top: 30px;">Welcome to our World of Highlights!</td></tr><tr><td colspan=4 style="font-family:Cailibri;line-height:25px;text-align: justify; font-size: 18px; color:#000; padding: 15px 30px;"><p>We're thrilled to have you join us on an extraordinary journey through Asia and beyond. Thank you for subscribing to our newsletter and showing interest in exploring the spectacular destinations.</p><p>As part of our community, you'll have exclusive access to insider travel tips, captivating destination inspirations, and exciting offers tailored to your wanderlust.</p><ul><li>Immerse yourself in the wonders of Asia, from vibrant cultures to stunning natural wonders at <a href="https://www.asiahighlights.com/?utm_source=newsletter&utm_medium=referral&utm_campaign=welcome" target="_blank" style="color: #000;">Highlights Travel</a>.</li><li>For global adventures, explore diverse destinations worldwide at <a href="https://www.globalhighlights.com/?utm_source=newsletter&utm_medium=referral&utm_campaign=welcome" target="_blank" style="color: #000;">Global Highlights</a>.</li><li>Discover the magic of Asia with its rich history and breathtaking landscapes at <a href="https://www.chinahighlights.com/?utm_source=newsletter&utm_medium=referral&utm_campaign=welcome" target="_blank" style="color: #000;">Highlights Travel</a>.</li></ul><p>We're passionate about curating extraordinary experiences that bring you closer to the heart of each destination. Feel free to <a href="https://www.asiahighlights.com/contact-us?utm_source=newsletter&utm_medium=referral&utm_campaign=autumn" target="_blank" style="color: #000;">reach out to us</a> if you have any questions or if there's anything we can assist you with.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=4><p style="font-size: 19px;color: #ad1818;font-weight: 600;padding: 0 30px;">Let the journey begin!</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=4><p style="font-size: 16px;color: #000;padding: 0 30px;">Warm regards,</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=4><p style="padding: 0 30px;font-size: 16px;color: #000;margin-top: -10px; margin-bottom: 40px;">Highlights Travel Team</p></td></tr></table></body></html>